name: tournament-tracker
description:
TournamentTracker

Tournament Tracking Application

I used a YouTube Tutorial at https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wfWxdh-_k_4 as a template for this application.

Significant changes from tutorial:

  • I used Azure SQL server instead of a local databse
  • I used HTML5 instead of WinForms
  • I enabled Azure AD Integrated Authentication
  • The SQL connection only has permissons to run stored procedures
